OL,6,FHe said: "The council does not have
OL,7,Fmoney lying around to tackle those
OL,8,Fsorts of things. The Government has
OL,9,Fhad this running for two years to
OL,10,Faddress the cost of living crisis,
OL,11,Fwhich in large part they contributed
OL,12,Fto through the Liz Truss fiscal event.
OL,14,F"The idea that they are going to
OL,15,Fwithdraw support at a time when
OL,16,Finflation is still high and we are in
OL,17,Fa recession is really shocking. The
OL,18,FGovernment needs to take
OL,19,Fresponsibility and keep the scheme
OL,20,Fgoing."
